{"tid":2397087,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上聯署呼籲澳洲公營電台　勿將廣東話台普通話台合併（附聯署連結）","createTime":"2021-02-06T06:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T07:15:36.000Z","uid":261647,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65cb4478277e9f582a08b46cbdd6e84093807d0c","tid":2397087,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T06:46:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3795926290464068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fposts%2F3795926290464068&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIflfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=a69d1a50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3795926290464068</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：港語學<br />\n<br />\n幫手簽！香港人都可以參與聯署！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/澳洲頻道-1.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%93-1.png%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1&h=7c0e98e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲公營嘅電台SBS一直都設有各種民族語言嘅頻道，包括普通話同廣東話，近日計劃將兩條頻道合併。有網民喺網上發起呼籲，促請SBS可以停止呢個合併嘅做法，並且質疑有關做法會破壞廣東話節目組編採自主。<br />\n<br />\n聯署發起人Alan Lo就寫話，喺澳洲同全球講廣東話嘅人，其實都對廣東話人嘅身分同語言受到嘅威脅感到擔憂，而最近見到有一筆資金入主導致廣東話台同普通話台合併。佢質疑既然電台多咗資金同資源，應該可以繼續開放兩條頻道，為澳洲嘅兩大華人社區服務。<br />\n<br />\n佢又話，SBS有單獨旁遮普語同北印度語嘅頻道同網頁，同樣道理都應該適用於保留廣東話台。<br />\n<br />\n佢又話新政策會同澳洲尊重多元文化同種族嘅精神背道而馳。既然澳洲放寬咗移民政策去容納被打壓嘅香港人，澳洲就會收納越嚟越多講廣東話嘅人。SBS係應該忠於服務各個族裔需求嘅使命。<br />\n<br />\n聯署連結:<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/sbs-australia-petition-against-merging-of-sbs-cantonese-and-mandarin-webpages-聯署反對sbs合併廣東話普通話網頁\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fsbs-australia-petition-against-merging-of-sbs-cantonese-and-mandarin-webpages-%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8Dsbs%E5%90%88%E4%BD%B5%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%A9%B1%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIflfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=7b5c8462\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/sbs-australia-petition-against-merging-of-sbs-cantonese-and-mandarin-webpages-聯署反對sbs合併廣東話普通話網頁</a>"},{"pid":"7fb9b5c0eccabb8a30b2219970ede3e6604675e0","tid":2397087,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858fa15ddc654e44014182d97cf90bbf2762a020","tid":2397087,"uid":314136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"合併做廣東話台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39d39c10aa6fdc26686405608ac8211616b5bda","tid":2397087,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"合併得呀,淨做廣東話！"}]}